"{\"uid\": \"ealingtimes.co.uk-news-24480718.josh-tarlings-olympic-comeback-cut-short-fourth-place-finish\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sport  Josh Tarling rued the mechanical misfortune which cost him an Olympic medal after finishing an agonising fourth in the men's time trial.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Madden\", \"score\": 0.9328876188879671, \"rank\": 0.07184596945346175, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Madden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Madden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 20-year-old west Walian had been tipped in some quarters to end Team GB's opening day gold drought which stretches back to Sydney 2000.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 213, \"end\": 220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.970187469143464, \"rank\": 0.030491571902898768, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2000_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999929259502, \"rank\": 7.074104315145265e-09, \"text\": \"Sydney 2000\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2000_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2000_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But a puncture early on in soaking conditions proved fatal as Tarling, despite battling admirably to stay in contention, finished an agonising 2.16 seconds adrift of a podium place.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Aberaeron native refused to indulge in speculation as to how much time the change of bike cost him but could not hide his inevitable disappointment.\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aberaeron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1150498496358375e-24, \"text\": \"Aberaeron\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aberaeron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aberaeron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It happens, does not it,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is not a lot I can do.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was hard to settle back down into a rhythm and stop thinking (about it) after that.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's easy to start flapping about and panicking but the car did a really good job of keeping me quiet and chilled out, I settled back into it.\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone who got a medal deserves it.\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I wanted it to go my way, I would have gone fast enough without a puncture to still win.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They all put the pressure on and there wasn't a lot I could do.\\\"\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling can perhaps take some consolation from the identity of the three men who finished ahead of him in a field stacked with quality.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A gutsy, brave and mature race which painfully just ends in a 4th placed finish for Josh Tarling in the men's time trial \\ud83d\\udc94The 20-year-old had to recover from a puncture to claw back time.You have done everyone proud, Josh!#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/SqXLHy8sdG  Serial world champions Filippo Ganna and Wout van Aert claimed silver and bronze behind Belgium's Remco Evenepoel, fresh from an impressive maiden Tour de France.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1344, \"end\": 1348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Madden\", \"score\": 0.9328876188879671, \"rank\": 0.07184596945346175, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Madden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Madden\"}, {\"begin\": 1478, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Madden\", \"score\": 0.9328876188879671, \"rank\": 0.07184596945346175, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Madden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Madden\"}, {\"begin\": 1544, \"end\": 1557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Filippo Ganna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\"}, {\"begin\": 1562, \"end\": 1575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wout van Aert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\"}, {\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5797678059175359, \"rank\": 0.7248284371364696, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Remco Evenepoel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Evenepoel, 24, slammed the condition of the roads used in the time trial after a practice ride earlier this week and claimed he spent 'all of Monday in bed' as he recovered from his Tour exertions.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would not blame him, to be honest,\\\" Tarling said.\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He had an amazing Tour.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was expecting it from him, he's such a classy rider and no-one can get close to him at the minute.\\\"\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling is not a man used to missing out on silverware in his fledgling career so far but his best years remain very much ahead of him.\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now based in Andorra, he may yet still leave Paris with a medal if he can bounce back in next Saturday's road race.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2217, \"end\": 2224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andorra\", \"score\": 0.9999999865449355, \"rank\": 1.0432628935545573e-08, \"text\": \"Andorra\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andorra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andorra\"}, {\"begin\": 2249, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999790816, \"rank\": 2.111174988062654e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will switch off tonight and switch back on as soon as I can,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will try and forget it but I will watch it back as a fan.\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They all did amazing rides and it was good to watch.\\\"\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aldi are proud Official Partners of Team GB & ParalympicsGB, supporting all athletes through to Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2512, \"end\": 2516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aldi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\"}, {\"begin\": 2608, \"end\": 2618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1885535800945095e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This website and associated newspapers adhere to the Independent Press Standards Organisation's     Editors' Code of Practice.\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have a complaint about the editorial content which relates to     inaccuracy or intrusion, then pleasecontact the editor here.\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are dissatisfied with the response provided you cancontact IPSO here  \\u00a9 2001-2025.\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2974, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ealing Timesis owned and operated by Newsquest Media Group Ltd, an audited local newspaper network.\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 3078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3017, \"end\": 3042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Newsquest Media Group Ltd\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Visitnewsquest.co.ukto view ourpoliciesandterms.\", 